=Please research this lead and generate a highly personalized "hyperLine". The line must prove we did our homework by mentioning a recent corporate event or milestone, and it must tie that event to the challenges they likely face in their specific role.

### TEMPORAL CONTEXT:
- Current Date: {{ $now.toFormat('yyyy-MM-dd') }}
- Target Year for News: {{ $now.toFormat('yyyy') }}

### SENDER CONTEXT:
- My Name: {{ $json.body.sender_context.senderName }}
- My Company: {{ $json.body.sender_context.senderCompany }}

### TARGET LEAD CONTEXT:
- Lead Name: {{ $json.body.lead_context.fullName }}
- Lead's Exact Role: {{ $json.body.lead_context.position }}
- Target Company: {{ $json.body.lead_context.companyName }}
- Website: {{ $json.body.lead_context.companyWebsite }}
- Company Linkedin Post:  {{ $json.body.lead_context.companyLinkedin }}/posts/?feedView=all
- Company Context: {{ $json.body.lead_context.companyDescription }}

### INSTRUCTIONS:
1. Search for news regarding {{ $json.body.lead_context.companyName }} in {{ $now.toFormat('yyyy') }} (or late {{ $now.minus({years: 1}).toFormat('yyyy') }}).
2. Write a single sentence that mentions a specific recent finding AND relates it to what they must be focusing on as the {{ $json.body.lead_context.position }}.
3. Ensure the sentence flows naturally so it can be seamlessly pasted into the very beginning of my email body.

parameters.jsCode:
// 1. Extract data from the Webhook and AI Agent
const webhookData = $('Webhook').first().json.body;
const aiData = $json.output;

// 2. Formatting: Convert "Enter" keystrokes to HTML line breaks
const baseBody = (webhookData.campaign_context.mainBody || "").replace(/\n/g, "<br>");
const aiLine = aiData.hyperLine || "";
const trackingId = webhookData.system_context.tracking_id;
const isSendMode = webhookData.system_context.delivery_mode === "send";
// Only build the tracking pixel if we are actually sending the email!
const pixel = isSendMode ? `<img src=' https://disarmingly-dashing-floy.ngrok-free.dev/t/o/${trackingId}.gif' width='1' height='1' style='display:none;' />` : "";

// 3. Inject the AI Hyperline into the exact placeholder spot
let finalContent = "";
const placeholder = "{{hyperline}}";

if (baseBody.includes(placeholder)) {
    finalContent = baseBody.replace(placeholder, aiLine);
} else {
    finalContent = aiLine + "<br><br>" + baseBody;
}

// 4. Build the Professional Email Signature
const senderName = webhookData.sender_context.senderName || "";
const senderRole = webhookData.sender_context.senderRole || "";
const senderCompany = webhookData.sender_context.senderCompany || "";
const senderAddress = webhookData.sender_context.senderAddress || "";

const signatureHtml = `<br><br>--<br><strong>${senderName}</strong><br>${senderRole} | ${senderCompany}<br>${senderAddress}`;

// 5. Build the core Microsoft Graph Message Object
const coreMessage = {
    subject: webhookData.campaign_context.subject,
    body: {
        contentType: "HTML",
        content: finalContent + signatureHtml + "<br><br>" + pixel
    },
    toRecipients: [
        {
            emailAddress: {
                address: webhookData.lead_context.email
            }
        }
    ]
};

// 6. Dynamic Attachment Logic
const attachmentData = webhookData.campaign_context.attachment;

// If Laravel provided an encoded file, inject it perfectly into the Microsoft Payload
if (attachmentData && attachmentData.contentBytes) {
    coreMessage.hasAttachments = true;
    coreMessage.attachments = [
        {
            "@odata.type": "#microsoft.graph.fileAttachment",
            "name": attachmentData.name || "document.pdf",
            "contentType": attachmentData.contentType || "application/pdf",
            "contentBytes": attachmentData.contentBytes
        }
    ];
}

// 7. Output the perfectly clean payloads to the next nodes
return {
    ms_graph_send_payload: { message: coreMessage, saveToSentItems: "true" },
    ms_graph_draft_payload: coreMessage,
    ms_graph_token: webhookData.system_context.microsoft_access_token,
    delivery_mode: webhookData.system_context.delivery_mode,
    callback_data: {
        campaign_recipient_id: webhookData.system_context.campaign_recipient_id,
        hyper_personalized_line: aiLine,
        news_summary: aiData.news_summary
    }
};
